Title: That's Pretty Gross
Description:
<You dislodge a familiar-looking appendage from the silt.

It doesn't seem particularly kobyss, but perhaps a unique specimen will earn you an increased reward from Al'kubian.>
ObjectivesText: Bring the Familiar-Looking Appendage back to Al'kubian.
RewardText:
You are what you eat.

And these kobyss are eating the strongest nerubians ever to Ascend. 

Don't mind the marks of moisture on the ground... That's my anxiety sweat.
